<p>Ethereum is an open-source, public, blockchain-based distributed computing platform featuring smart contract (scripting) functionality. It provides a decentralized virtual machine, the Ethereum Virtual Machine (EVM).</p>

<p>ETC or ETH “Classic” is worth steadily about 10% of ETH and it is the underlying asset of the proposed <a href="https://grayscale.co/ethereum-investment-trust/">Ethereum ETF</a>.</p>

<h4>Trading Ether and Ether Classic</h4>

<p>You can trade ETH and ETC on <a class="external" rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="https://poloniex.com">Poloniex</a> with fees of .15%/.25% and also on <a class="external" rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="https://www.bitfinex.com/?refcode=5egV78YtlC">Bitfinex - sign up with this link to get the generous fees of .09%/.18%</a>. Charts and indicators are available on <a class="external" rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://tradingview.go2cloud.org/SHW9">TradingView</a>.</p>

